<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport">
    <title>Casa Benedita</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Restaurante Dona Benedita - Comida caseira e saudável.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="restaurante, comida caseira, dona benedita">

    <link href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Amatic+SC:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href=""
          rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="../wwwroot/assets/vendor/bootstrap-icons/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="../wwwroot/js/assets/vendor/aos/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="../wwwroot/js/assets/vendor/glightbox/css/glightbox.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="~/wwwroot/js/assets/vendor/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="~/css/site.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body class="index-page">

 
    

    <header id="header" class="header-overlay d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="container d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="logo d-flex align-items-center">
                <img src="~/Images/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo-icon">
                <h1 class="logo-text">CASA BENEDITA</h1>
            </a>

            <nav id="navmenu" class="navmenu">
                <ul>
                    <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">INÍCIO</a></li>
                    <li><a asp-controller="Cardapio" asp-action="Index">CARDÁPIO</a></li>
                    <li><a asp-controller="Reserva" asp-action="Index">RESERVAS</a></li>
                    <li class="d-lg-none"><a href="#" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#loginModal">ENTRAR</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>

            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                <a href="#" class="btn-entrar d-none d-lg-block" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#loginModal">ENTRAR</a>
                <i class="mobile-nav-toggle d-xl-none bi bi-list" style="font-size: 32px; color: #fff; cursor: pointer;"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero-full">
            <img src="~/Images/Fachada.png" alt="Banner" class="hero-bg">
            <div class="hero-container">
                <div class="hero-content" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <h2>Faça sua Reserva</h2>
                    <p>Garanta seu lugar com mais conforto.</p>
                    <a asp-controller="Reserva" asp-action="Index" class="btn-book">RESERVE AGORA SUA MESA</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about" class="about section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row gy-4">
                    <div class="col-lg-7" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                        <img src="~/Images/COZINHA.png" class="img-fluid mb-4" alt="Interior do restaurante">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="250">
                        <div class="content ps-0 ps-lg-5">
                            <p class="fst-italic">
                                Na Dona Benedita, acreditamos que a comida une as pessoas. Nossa jornada começou com receitas de família passadas por gerações.
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> <span>Ingredientes frescos colhidos no dia.</span></li>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> <span>Ambiente acolhedor e familiar para seus amigos.</span></li>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> <span>Pratos feitos na hora com temperos naturais.</span></li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>
                                Trabalhamos duro para garantir que cada garfada seja uma lembrança afetiva. Do nosso fogão para a sua mesa, sempre com o carinho que você merece.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer-pro">
        <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="footer-col">
                <p>
                    <strong>Localização:</strong><br>
                    Rua Barão de Capanema, 2900<br>
                    Jardins - São Paulo | SP
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Reservas:</strong><br>
                    21 2493-2021 | 21 2494-7418
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>E-mail:</strong><br>
                    CasaBenedita@gmail.com.br
                </p>
                <div class="social">
                    <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
                    <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h3>Como Chegar</h3>
                <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3657.197502758151!2d-46.663189!3d-23.561349!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x0!2zMjPCsDMzJzQwLjkiUyA0NsKwMzknNDcuNSJX!5e0!3m2!1spt-BR!2sbr!4v1620000000000!5m2!1spt-BR!2sbr" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-col">
                <h3>Funcionamento</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><span>Segunda</span> 11:30h às 23:45h</li>
                    <li><span>Terça</span> 11:30h às 23:45h</li>
                    <li><span>Quarta</span> 11:30h às 23:45h</li>
                    <li><span>Quinta</span> 11:30h às 23:45h</li>
                    <li><span>Sexta</span> 11:30h às 23:45h</li>
                    <li><span>Sábado</span> 11:30h às 01:00h</li>
                    <li><span>Domingo</span> 11:30h às 23:45h</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="../wwwroot/js/assets/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../wwwroot/js/assets/vendor/aos/aos.js"></script>
    <script src="../wwwroot/js/assets/vendor/glightbox/js/glightbox.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../wwwroot/js/assets/vendor/purecounter/purecounter_vanilla.js"></script>
    <script src="../wwwroot/js/assets/vendor/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../wwwroot/js/main.js"></script>

</body>
</html>